Michael Lassen: 19. February 1998

NEW FILE: aliases.bet
	- Interface to the alias manager (not yet complete)
	
NEW FILE: icons.bet
	- Interface to the iconsuite manager (not yet complete)
	

******************************************************************
Michael Lassen: 27. January 98

Started to use the CHANGES file.

Some of the changes are caused by renames in apples universal 
headers. For now the old name is kept when possible. A scheme
should be invented to aid developers in updating applications
to use the new names. 

FILE: AppleEvents.bet

	* Changed the interface of AESend from
	
		AESend: External
		  (# theAppleEvent,reply: ^AppleEvent;
			 sendMode,timeOutInTicks: @Integer;
			 idleProc,filterProc: ##External;
			 sendPriority,OSErr: @ShortInt;
		  enter (theAppleEvent[],reply[],sendMode,sendPriority,timeOutInTicks,idleProc##,filterProc##)
		  do ...
		  exit OSErr
		  #);
		  
	  to
	  
		AESend: External
		  (# theAppleEvent,reply: ^AppleEvent;
			 sendMode,timeOutInTicks: @Integer;
			 idleProc,filterProc: @integer;
			 sendPriority,OSErr: @ShortInt;
		  enter (theAppleEvent[],reply[],sendMode,sendPriority,timeOutInTicks,idleProc,filterProc)
		  do ...
		  exit OSErr
		  #);
	
	  This allows 0 (NULL) to be given as idleProc and filterProc.
	  use myFilterProc## -> MakeCBF when needed.


FILE: controlmanager.bet

	* Rename: useWFont => kControlUsesOwningWindowsFontVariant
	
FILE: macdirectory.bet
	  morefiles.bet

	* BUILD directive changed to support shared libraries.
	
FILE: menus.bet

	* New Procedure: InvalMenuBar

FILE: opentransport.bet
	  opentransportglue.c
	  
	* These files are deleted, since they did not contain
	  a real interface to opentransport.
	  
FILE: quickdraw.bet

	* Added top, left, right, bottom, bounds to polygonPtr

FILE: textedit.bet

	* New constants: teFlushDefault, teCenter, teFlushRight, teFlushLeft

FILE: Appearance.bet

	* New file that interfaces the new Apperance Manager. The interface
	  is not complete.


